Global Scope (~/.gemini/skills/ or .agents/skills/): Available across all Antigravity products (Antigravity, Antigravity IDE, Antigravity CLI) and projects.
Product Scope: If you like that your skills should be available only to Antigravity or to the Antigravity CLI product, then you will have to put them inside the respective skills folder of the product. For Antigravity, this would be ~/.gemini/antigravity/skills/ and for Antigravity CLI, this would be ~/.gemini/antigravity-cli/skills/
Project/Workspace Scope (<project-root>/.agents/skills/): This would make the skill available only within a specific project.




